峰讲升学规划」直播间，自 9 月份以来图书类目销售额已达 2500 万—5000 万元（其他平台渠道及账号未统计在内），其关联店铺「峰阅万卷」图书销售额已超过 5000 万元。 资料来源张雪峰 2025 届志愿填报开抢，售价 12999 元—18999 元，上架 20 分钟多省份名额售罄"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-92ce5adfd616464ab78b9e998dc0f77b_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "126 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1890105476693332026"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI4dX3/IOz5eINEAMaCTExNDI2NTI5NyDG16m/BjAAOFxAA3ITMTg5MDEwNTQ3NjY5MzMzMjAyNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1743635450.596580", "card_id": "Q_1888685528414660511", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "黄金价格会不会迎来暴跌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2025 年以来，金价的价格一路飙升上涨，再接下来会不会迎来一次大跌？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-30e1274542bb5540f711f7c47edf1995_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "126 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1888685528414660511"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4dX3/IOz5eINEAMaCTExNDIwMzc2MCDYgpW/BjAAONwBQARyEzE4ODg2ODU1Mjg0MTQ2NjA1MTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1743635450.596859", "card_id": "Q_1890355890814693856", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待大批洋垃圾企图入境，已被南京金陵海关截获，其中包含 840 件日本旧和服，